column2: SELECT TOP # y.r, y.g, p.oiii_#_reqw_err as oir_e, p.h_beta_reqw_err as hbr_e, p.nii_#_reqw_err as nir_e, p.h_alpha_reqw_err as har_e, oiii_#_reqw as oir, h_beta_reqw as hbr, nii_#_reqw as nir, h_alpha_reqw as har, p.specObjID, zs.nvote, zs.p_el as elliptical, zs.p_cw as spiralclock, zs.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zs.p_edge as edgeon, zs.p_dk as dontknow, zs.p_mg as merger         FROM galSpecLine as p    JOIN ZooSpec AS zs ON p.specObjID = zs.specobjid    JOIN Galaxy as y ON p.specObjID = y.specObjID    WHERE zs.nvote >= # and zs.p_m >#
